<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-94-1345 </DOCNO><TEXT>Tension Leg Platforms (TLP) became a reality with the installation ofthe Conoco Hutton TLP. Many oil companies now consider TLPs as a viabledevelopment option particularly for deeper water. One critical area ofTLP design is the riser system and riser related subsea equipment. Thispaper outlines the work undertaken to establish a viable riser systemcomponents, riser analysis and the installation of control lines insiderisers. 14 drawings, 3 tables.</TEXT></DOC>